&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pursuing a Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Cybersecurity, CS, IS, IT, or other related fields of studyExpected/achieved minimum 2:1 classification in a Computer Science, Cybersecurity, Engineering or related degree discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Visualization and Dashboarding:&lt;/strong&gt; Expertise in tools such as Power BI, Tableau, R Shiny, or Google Data Studio to develop interactive data dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Engineering and ETL:&lt;/strong&gt; Competence in SQL, Python, or R for data manipulation, retrieval, cleansing, and structuring from various sources (e.g., databases, APIs, Excel, GRC platforms).&lt;/li&gt;
