&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Procurement Analyst Intern&lt;/strong&gt; to help us improve how we track company spending and manage performance metrics. This role is focused on data integrity and visualization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spend Dashboard Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Consolidate and clean large sets of purchasing data to build interactive dashboards. You will help visualize Who, What, and Where we spend to identify cost-saving opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contract Performance Tracking:&lt;/strong&gt; Analyze the Cycle Time of our end to end procurement process &amp;amp; build a tracking dashboard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Process Bottleneck Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify stages in the procurement process that cause delays and provide data-backed suggestions on how to speed them up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Integrity:&lt;/strong&gt; Audit and scrub procurement databases to ensure all information is accurate, categorized correctly, and up to date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements &amp;amp; Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education:&lt;/strong&gt; Currently pursuing or recently completed a degree in &lt;strong&gt;Supply Chain Management, Finance, Economics, Business Analytics,&lt;/strong&gt; or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; * Advanced proficiency in &lt;strong&gt;Microsoft Excel&lt;/strong&gt; (VLOOKUPs, Pivot Tables, and Data Visualization are a must).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with BI tools (like Tableau or Power BI) is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytical Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; A knack for spotting patterns in messy data and translating them into actionable insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Integrity:&lt;/strong&gt; High level of ethical standards, as you will be dealing with sensitive financial information and vendor contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
