&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Available location(s): &lt;/strong&gt;Singapore&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Cloudflare&#39;s Solutions Engineers come from all kinds of backgrounds: software development, computer science, data science, networking, and plenty of fields that have nothing obvious to do with technology. What we hire for isn&#39;t a specific degree. It&#39;s a mindset: curious, technically sharp, and motivated by helping others succeed. We&#39;re the technical customer advocates within Cloudflare, working closely with Sales, Product, Engineering, and Customer Support with one shared goal: customer success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The APAC Solutions Engineering, Center of Excellence (COE) is a small, focused team within the broader APAC SE organisation. Right now, we&#39;re building the AI capabilities that will change how SE, Sales, and GTM teams work across the region. We&#39;re looking for interns who want to be part of building that.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You&#39;re probably finishing a degree, or close to it, in &lt;strong&gt;computer science, software engineering, data science&lt;/strong&gt;, or something in that space. But your best work probably didn&#39;t happen in a lecture theatre. It happened when you stayed up debugging a side project, shipped something at a hackathon, or found yourself reading documentation for a technology you had no real reason to know yet.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for curious and ambitious builders who want to explore a career that mixes technical depth with helping others do their best work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Curious what the programme looks like in practice? &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.cloudflare.com/tag/internship-experience/&quot;&gt;Hear directly from our past interns.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll join Cloudflare&#39;s APAC Solutions Engineering, Center of Excellence (COE) team as part of a small cohort of interns working directly with the team running an internal AI initiative. The goal is to build AI capabilities across SE, Sales, and GTM functions in APAC. This isn&#39;t a shadow-and-observe internship. You&#39;ll build real tools, contribute to live projects, and leave behind work that your colleagues actually use.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;All the resources and training required to be effective in this role will be provided.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In a typical week, you might:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Build and test an AI agent or internal chatbot to help SE and Sales teams work faster, built on Cloudflare Workers AI and AI Gateway&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Design and prototype a demo that shows Cloudflare&#39;s AI platform capabilities for a real customer use case&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Write scripts or lightweight tools that cut manual work out of GTM workflows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Dig into usage or productivity data to see what impact the tools your team built are actually having&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Present your work at a team showcase or sprint review&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ship at least one internal AI tool that SE or GTM colleagues are actively using&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Contribute to tools or demos that make a real difference to how the team works&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Leave with at least one piece of work the wider team can pick up and use&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is critical that you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Can write working code in Python, JavaScript, or a similar language and ship things independently&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Have a basic understanding of how the web works: HTTP, REST APIs, DNS, TLS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Can explain what you built and why, to a technical or non-technical audience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Are curious and self-directed. You try things before asking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Able to commit to a minimum 12 week summer internship from May to August 2026&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Able to work from office 3-5 days a week in Singapore&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It would be awesome if you also:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Have played around with LLMs, AI APIs, or prompt engineering, even just in side projects, coursework, or a hackathon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
