&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: &lt;/strong&gt;Industry Focused Analyst Intern&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The CxO Transformation Partners (CXTP) team serves as trusted advisors to Cloudflare’s most senior customers and prospects. We are a highly strategic group who simplify technical complexity and align our solutions with large-scale business objectives. Our mission is to unlock commercial outcomes by bridging the gap between deep technical capabilities and executive-level strategic goals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Internship&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role focuses on owning in-depth industry research and competitive landscape analysis to enhance the team’s ability to tailor solutions and messaging to key markets. Key deliverables include reports on cybersecurity trends, comprehensive offering-to-industry mapping, and competitive analysis. You will enable more informed and targeted executive customer engagements and contribute to thought leadership content, positioning Cloudflare as a leader in verticalized cybersecurity. Everything created will see tangible impact on executive briefings, sales enablement materials (playbooks/battlecards), and internal knowledge bases for the CXTP team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Get To Do In This Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Own the dedicated industry research and competitive landscape analysis necessary to enhance the team’s ability to tailor solutions and messaging to key markets. The expected outcomes of this internship include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Research Reports:&lt;/strong&gt; Deliver reports on cybersecurity trends, threats, and regulatory landscapes for target industries (e.g., Aviation and Transportation, Finance, Healthcare, Retail, etc.), identifying key challenges and opportunities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cloudflare Offering-to-Industry Mapping:&lt;/strong&gt; Create comprehensive mapping documents that align Cloudflare&#39;s current and potential product capabilities with the specific cybersecurity needs and pain points of the researched industries. This will include identifying gaps and areas for new solution development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Conduct an analysis of niche competitors focused on the researched industries, highlighting their strengths, weaknesses, and how Cloudflare&#39;s offerings compare.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Improved Sales Enablement:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to the creation of industry-specific CxO level playbooks, presentations, and battlecards enabling more informed and targeted customer engagements for the Field CXO team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Briefing Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist in the preparation of research summaries and presentation materials for executive-level customer engagements, demonstrating Cloudflare&#39;s understanding of industry-specific challenges and its ability to provide relevant solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thought Leadership Contributions:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute research findings and insights to internal knowledge bases, and potentially assist in drafting external-facing content (e.g., blog posts, whitepapers) that positions Cloudflare as a thought leader in verticalized cybersecurity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Presentation to Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Present findings and recommendations to the Field CxO team and relevant stakeholders, demonstrating the business impact and learning value derived from the internship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing an Undergrad BA/BS or Masters MA/MS (MBA not required).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Available for a full-time 12-week internship, working from our Lisbon office 3-5 days a week during the summer (May-Aug).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience or strong interest in conducting in-depth market research and competitive analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to own a high-impact project end-to-end and deliver portfolio-ready results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and presentation skills. This role demands someone who is gifted in their ability to communicate effectively with all stakeholders, including executives, sales, and marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-starter who truly enjoys working in a fast-paced, innovative cloud services company.&lt;/li&gt;
